@startuml
title LifeDuo - Descricao de Atores
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Parceiro A" as PartnerA
actor "Parceiro B" as PartnerB
actor "Administrador" as Admin
actor "Gateway de Pagamento" as Payment
actor "Firebase Cloud Messaging" as FCM
actor "Servicos de Mapa" as Maps

rectangle "Sistema LifeDuo" as System {
}

PartnerA --> System
PartnerB --> System
Admin --> System
Payment --> System
FCM --> System
Maps --> System

note right of PartnerA
Usuário principal do app:
- check-in
- metas
- presentes
end note

note right of PartnerB
Mesmo papel funcional do Parceiro A
com dados compartilhados por casal.
end note

@enduml
